reviews.title: Terrible
reviews.comment: Must be part of Monday family data? The dragons are limited and boring, they lag, stop unexpectedly, I downloaded a bunch of them and then learn that the variety, which is the only thing that makes these pitiful wallpapers worth the time, is limited, and to enjoy them all you must download another app that doesn\'t allow your phone to sleep and devours the battery.  Uninstalled them all. Waste of time.
reviews.author: Lia LeFae
